<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Nicholas Fason is a passionate and driven student, developer, and novice researcher. He is currently pursuing a Bachelor's of Arts in Computer Science with a minor in Communication Studies at <a href="https://uab.edu" rel="external">the University of Alabama at Birmingham</a>. After graduation, he plans to pursue a Master's of Arts in Communication Studies with a focus on the intersection of technology, communication, and medical science. He's currently in his 3rd year at UAB, graduating by May 2025. 
